  <brief_title>A Study to Compare Effectiveness of Montelukast Sodium With Comparator in Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthmatics (0476-329)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open Label, Cross-Over Study Comparing Effectiveness for the Montelukast Sodium With Comparator in Mild to Moderate Persistent Asthmatics</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</agency>
      <agency_class>Industry</agency_class>
    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Merck Sharp &amp; Dohme Corp.</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Subjects have 8-week with montelukast sodium or comparator drug administration period, 2-week
      wash-out period and 8-week comparator drug or the drug administration period (with cross-over
      design) for assessment of the drug efficacy, safety and tolerability.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
